OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FAdult adoptees have spoken about their
OL,7,F'traumatising' experiences trying to
OL,8,Ffind out basic information, ITV News
OL,9,FSocial Affairs Correspondent Sarah
OL,10,FCorker & Senior Producer Lottie
OL,11,FKilraine report
OL,13,FThe UK's Information regulator (ICO)
OL,14,Fhas warned councils could face legal
OL,15,Faction over long delays, errors and
OL,16,Fmissing documents for those trying to
OL,17,Faccess their adoption files and care
OL,18,Frecords, in an exclusive interview
OL,19,Fwith ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
