OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FThe Information Commissioner John
OL,7,FEdwards has written to all UK local
OL,8,Fauthority leaders warning them of
OL,9,Ftheir legal duties and said these
OL,10,Frecords can help to "unlock a person's
OL,11,Fidentity" and "uncomfortable truths"
OL,12,Fthat matter to society.
OL,14,FAs part of an ongoing investigation by
OL,15,FITV News into forced adoptions in the
OL,16,F1950s, 60s and 70s, we have spoken to
OL,17,Fadult adoptees across Britain about
OL,18,Ftheir "traumatising" experiences
OL,19,Ftrying to find out basic information
OL,20,Fabout the circumstances around their
OL,21,Fbirth and adoption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
