OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FZara Phillips told ITV News she feels
OL,7,F'frustrated' after she was told her
OL,8,Fadoption file is still incomplete and
OL,9,Fsome records are missing with little
OL,10,Fexplanation as to why, after years of
OL,11,Ffighting to get access
OL,13,FZara Phillips, 61, from North London
OL,14,Fwaited for 18 months for an
OL,15,Fappointment with a social worker after
OL,16,Frequesting access to her adoption and
OL,17,Fcare records from the council.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FWhen she did eventually receive her
OL,7,Fdocuments earlier this month, she was
OL,8,Falso told her file was still
OL,9,Fincomplete and some records were
OL,10,Fmissing with little explanation why.
OL,12,F"Living with the unknown is like
OL,13,Ftorture," Ms Phillips told ITV News.
OL,15,F"I should have been given this years
OL,16,Fago, this is rightfully mine.
OL,17,FEverything written on these pieces of
OL,18,Fpaper is about me. I am frustrated and
OL,19,Fdisappointed. What are they trying to
OL,20,Fhide?"
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@IO]wD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
