OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FIn the 1980s she traced and reunited
OL,7,Fwith her birth mother, and later found
OL,8,Fher father, but gaps about her
OL,9,Fchildhood remained.
OL,11,FMs Phillips learned through her files
OL,12,Fthat her "mother never even got a
OL,13,Fchance to say goodbye to me". At just
OL,14,Fa few days old, she was taken from her
OL,15,Fmother when she was receiving life-
OL,16,Fsaving treatment after labour in
OL,17,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
