OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FZara Phillips, who is a singer and
OL,7,Fmusician, has written a song about the
OL,8,Fsuffering faced by victims and
OL,9,Fsurvivors of the forced adoption
OL,10,Fscandal and the continued fight for
OL,11,Fjustice for all those affected
OL,13,FShe is far from alone. For many
OL,14,Fsurvivors of the forced adoption era
OL,15,Faccess to records remains a major
OL,16,Fissue with lengthy delays, unexplained
OL,17,Fredactions and missing files all too
OL,18,Fcommon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
