OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FAdopted people have had a right to
OL,7,Faccess their adoption records since
OL,8,F1976, but there are huge disparities
OL,9,Facross England.
OL,11,FCouncils have a legal duty to respond
OL,12,Fto requests for personal information,
OL,13,Fbut a backlog of cases, short
OL,14,Fstaffing, fragmented paper records
OL,15,Facross councils, courts, and other
OL,16,Fagencies can result in delays and
OL,17,Ferrors, with no national protocol
OL,18,Fdespite repeated calls for reform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
