OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FThe Information Commissioner John
OL,7,FEdwards has warned local authorities
OL,8,Fthat there needs to be a step change
OL,9,Fin how councils respond to requests
OL,10,Ffor records.
OL,12,F"I have some sympathy with local
OL,13,Fauthorities," Mr Edwards told ITV News.
OL,15,F"They have a lot of duties, a lot of
OL,16,Fresponsibilities. But this is not
OL,17,Foptional. This is not voluntary. This
OL,18,Fis a statutory obligation.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,F"And if they don't resource it in a
OL,7,Fway that means they can meet people's
OL,8,Fstatutory rights, then we can come
OL,9,Fafter them. It is completely
OL,10,Funacceptable to wait two years," he
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FJohn Edwards, the UK's Information
OL,14,FCommissioner, told ITV News it is a
OL,15,F'statutory obligation' that
OL,16,Fauthorities help people access their
OL,17,Fpersonal information
OL,26,@rD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
