OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FFollowing 63 complaints, the ICO
OL,7,Frecently served Bristol City Council
OL,8,Fwith an enforcement notice for delays
OL,9,Fand a consistent backlog since 2020 in
OL,10,Fresponding to child social care data
OL,11,Frequests.
OL,13,FIt also fined the Scottish charity
OL,14,FBirthlink #18,000 after it destroyed
OL,15,F4,800 personal records, including
OL,16,Fhandwritten letters and photographs.
OL,18,FHowever this type of enforcement
OL,19,Faction is rare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FMr Edwards explained that the ICO's
OL,7,Fgoal is to work with councils to
OL,8,Fensure there is a degree of compassion
OL,9,Fwhen responding to these requests, and
OL,10,Fultimately fines come out of public
OL,11,Fcoffers and already stretched budgets.
OL,13,FFor some the search information has
OL,14,Flasted a lifetime and has been a
OL,15,F"complete nightmare".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
