OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FVerity Spencer-Natalello, who is 67,
OL,7,Fwas born in the 1950s to an unmarried
OL,8,Fmother in the Midlands, and adopted at
OL,9,Fseven weeks old. Her childhood was a
OL,10,Fhappy one but questions over identity
OL,11,Fwere never far away.
OL,13,FAfter a series of errors, she finally
OL,14,Ffound out for certain who her father
OL,15,Fwas in November - by which time he had
OL,16,Falready died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FVerity Spencer-Natalello only realised
OL,7,Finformation that she was entitled to
OL,8,Fhad been held back after watching an
OL,9,FITV News report in July, describing it
OL,10,Fas a 'lightbulb' moment
OL,12,FShe had only realised information that
OL,13,Fshe was entitled to had been held back
OL,14,Fafter watching an ITV News report in
OL,15,FJuly, describing it as a "lightbulb"
OL,16,Fmoment.
OL,18,FThe toll on her mental health has been
OL,19,Fconsiderable as she described a
OL,20,Fshattered sense of identity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
