PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,F"I still don't know who I am. I don't
OL,7,Ffeel like I belong in any family," she
OL,8,Ftold ITV News.
OL,10,F"I am an upbeat personality, but it
OL,11,Fhas brought me to the brink. I've been
OL,12,Fon the verge of suicide on two
OL,13,Foccasions that I can think of,
OL,14,Fseriously."
OL,16,FAt times her search for answers has
OL,17,Fbeen met with long stretches of
OL,18,Fsilence and errors by the public
OL,19,Fbodies, including three different
OL,20,Fcouncils, whose job it is to provide
OL,21,Fvital information.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@bO]rD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,F"I've said to them 'are you waiting
OL,7,Ffor me to drop down dead?' I've been
OL,8,Fvery blunt," Ms Spencer-Natalello said.
OL,10,F"I was a nobody right from the word
OL,11,Fgo, but I'm not a nobody, so treat me
OL,12,Fwith a bit of respect.
OL,14,F"You are infantilised forever. If they
OL,15,Fwould just give you the information
OL,16,Fthat you should have right at the
OL,17,Fbeginning, right when you should have
OL,18,Fit, and stop all this messing about
OL,19,Fand all the lies."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]rD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
