OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FBefore 1976, there were no laws
OL,7,Fsetting out how long records should be
OL,8,Fkept, and some have been destroyed
OL,9,Fover time.
OL,11,FWhen asked whether he was concerned
OL,12,Fthat organisations involved in
OL,13,Fhistoric forced adoptions - including
OL,14,Fcharities and religious groups, seem
OL,15,Fto have a high incidence of missing
OL,16,Ffiles and natural disasters like fires
OL,17,Fand floods - Mr Edwards said simply:
OL,18,F"There is no evidence this is being
OL,19,Fdone wilfully."
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
