CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FReligious organisations involved in
OL,7,Fthese adoptions and running mother and
OL,8,Fbaby institutions such as the Catholic
OL,9,FChurch, Church of England and
OL,10,FSalvation Army have to comply with
OL,11,Fdata laws on how they handle and store
OL,12,Ffiles, but unlike councils they are
OL,13,Funder no legal obligation to share
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FAdult adoptees and birth mothers have
OL,17,Fvoiced their frustrations about the
OL,18,Flack of transparency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
