OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the campaign group
OL,7,Fthe Adult Adoptee Movement said: "When
OL,8,Fyou are adopted, every scrap of
OL,9,Finformation about your early life
OL,10,Fmatters.
OL,12,F"Adoption records shed light on our
OL,13,Ffirst families and the circumstances
OL,14,Fsurrounding our removal. They may
OL,15,Fcontain information on our medical
OL,16,Fhistory, wider family, culture and
OL,17,Fheritage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
