OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772110991
OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,F"Adoptees face confusion about where
OL,7,Fdocuments are held and how to access
OL,8,Fthem. Long delays and inappropriate
OL,9,Fredactions are common.
OL,11,F"We join the Archives and Records
OL,12,FAssociation in their call for a review
OL,13,Fof current preservation arrangements
OL,14,Fand a centralised database of
OL,15,Fholdings."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@JO]
