OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FDiana Defries, who was forced to give
OL,7,Fup her baby aged 16 and campaigns for
OL,8,Fthe Movement for an Adoption Apology
OL,9,F(MAA), said: "Records are too often
OL,10,Flost or damaged, misplaced, misfiled
OL,11,For excessively redacted.
OL,13,F"All files relating to historic forced
OL,14,Fadoption practices must be protected
OL,15,Ffrom harm and made available so that
OL,16,Fthe truth about what was done to us
OL,17,Fand to our children can be revealed."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/25
