OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FIn response to the points raised in
OL,7,Fthis report, the Local Government
OL,8,FAssociation (LGA) said councils "will
OL,9,Fact with compassion and do all they
OL,10,Fcan to ensure adult adoptees have
OL,11,Faccess to their complete adoption
OL,12,Frecords without delay".
OL,14,FThe LGA put ongoing delays down to
OL,15,F"older records being generally paper-
OL,16,Fbased which can take longer to locate".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/25
