OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the government
OL,7,Fsaid: "People who have been adopted
OL,8,Fdeserve timely and compassionate
OL,9,Fsupport, and it is extremely
OL,10,Fconcerning that some still face
OL,11,Funcertainty.
OL,13,F"We have written to all Regional
OL,14,FAdoption Agencies, Voluntary Adoption
OL,15,FAgencies and local authorities to
OL,16,Fremind them of the need to respond
OL,17,Ffully and promptly to requests.
