OL,3,C'It's like torture': The long battle
OL,4,Cfor adoption records access
OL,6,F"Adoption England's guidance on this
OL,7,Fis clear, and through Family Connect
OL,8,Fwe are funding a national service that
OL,9,Fhelps adopted adults locate and access
OL,10,Ftheir records."
